#Resolving Git line ending issues in containers (resulting in many modified files)
#Linux
* text=auto eol=lf

#Windows
*.{cmd,[cC][mM][dD]} text eol=crlf
*.{bat,[bB][aA][tT]} text eol=crlf



# General #
###########
* text=auto


